djtalbrazilianregister.additionalDescription:
The storeowner has total control over the requested information in the registration form. <em>CPF </em>and <em>CNPJ </em>&nbsp;can be configured as obligatory fields.<br />
The module will verify if the informed <em>CPF </em>or the<em> CNPJ </em>are correct. This information should be trustworthy for the issue of the Brazilian <em>Nota Fiscal</em>.<br />
The <em>CEP </em>can be used to obtain the client&rsquo;s address. For clients that don&rsquo;t know their <em>CEP </em>there is an option for the storeowner to display a &ldquo;I don&rsquo;t know my <em>CEP</em>&rdquo; button. This will redirect the customer to <em>Correios</em> website to get help.&nbsp;
